380→    /// CancellationToken.  Cancelling it restarts the bot polling loop with
381→    /// offset 0, causing Telegram to re-deliver the OTP code message.  The
382→    /// re-delivered message would pass access control (user is now on the
383→    /// allowlist) and get forwarded to the LLM.
